text: "Barbie Tingz" is a hip hop song by Trinidadian-American rapper Nicki Minaj, released on April 12, 2018. The song has been included as an additional track on the Target and Japanese exclusive versions of Minaj's fourth studio album, Queen. Commercially, the song managed to peak at number one in New Zealand. ==References== Category:Nicki Minaj songs Category:Hip hop songs Category:2018 songs
